. I need thee every hour, most gracious Lord;
no tender voice like thine can peace afford.
Refrain:
I need thee, O I need thee;
every hour I need thee;
O bless me now, my Savior, I come to thee.. I need thee every hour; stay thou nearby;
temptations lose their power when thou art nigh.
(Refrain). I need thee every hour, in joy or pain;
come quickly and abide, or life is vain.
(Refrain). I need thee every hour; teach me thy will;
and thy rich promises in me fulfill.
(Refrain). I need thee every hour, most Holy One;
O make me thine indeed, thou blessed Son.
